==Legacy==
Mabel's death had a profound impact on her son's faith. Years later, Tolkien wrote: "My own dear mother was a martyr indeed, and it is not to everybody that God grants so easy a way to His great gifts as He did to Hilary and myself, giving us a mother who killed herself with labour and trouble to ensure us keeping the faith."<ref name=biography />{{rp|39}}

In the 2019 biographical drama film ''[[Tolkien (film)|Tolkien]]'', Mabel was portrayed by actress Laura Donnelly.
